description:
星垂智能 ZENO 是一家总部在西安的科技创业公司，由连续创业者们创立，创始人们曾在美国，阿联酋等地工作和创业。目前 ZENO 处于影藏模式中，已经获得来自阿联酋，加拿大和新加坡的客户。公司位于西安，并在迪拜设有分公司。
公司提供完善的福利制度和行业内 Top 5% 的薪资。我们期望新同事拥有良好的英文沟通能力，对新技术的敏锐性和对新鲜事物的好奇心。

Job Responsibilities
1. Provide full spectrum of administrative support to general manager, including but not limited to internal and external meetings scheduling, business and private reception and travel arrangements;
2. Responsible for the preparation of conference materials, conference management and preparing meeting minutes and reports;
3. Assist in preparing presentation materials and speeches for public events and media interviews;
4. Assist in arranging monthly expenses, making expense report and dealing with the reimbursement;
5. Closely work and communicate with clients and internal parties to resolve problems;
6. Perform tasks as assigned.

Job Requirements
1. Bachelor's degree or above from a well-recognized university (local & overseas);
2. 3 years of tech industry work experience, familiar with business etiquette,
3. Good command of spoken and written Chinese and English;
4. Well-organized, motivated and detail-minded
5.Basic schedule management, information processing, reimbursement management, document processing, administrative management, meeting/event support capabilities;
6. Proficiency PC knowledge in office software, excellent PowerPoint presentation skills;
7. Honest, fast learner with strong sense of responsibility.

